Name: Corio
Description: The Division of Corio consists of part of the Greater Geelong City Council.
ProductsAndIndustry: Health and allied services, education and research, manufacturing, tourism, agribusiness, construction and business services.
NameDerivation: Named after the geographic area covered by the electoral division. 'Corio' is beleved to have originated from an Aboriginal word 'coraiyo' meaning small marsupial or sandy cliffs or from the Aboriginal word 'Korayn' meaning salt.
